
---

### ✅ Step 4: **Choose a License**

Create a `LICENSE` file. The MIT License is usually best for code. Use [this template](https://choosealicense.com/licenses/mit/).

---

### ✅ Step 5: **Optional but Recommended — Create a Citation File**

Create a file called `CITATION.cff` with this:

```yaml
cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Smart Industry AI Framework
authors:
  - family-names: Bartolomeu
    given-names: Eduardo Enoque Nassimba
    affiliation: Independent Researcher
date-released: 2025-06-10
url: https://github.com/eduardo-bartolomeu/smart-industry-ai-framework
version: 1.0.0
